replacement for Giuliani was Rep. Rick A. Lazio, a Long Island
Republican.
</P>
<P>
   _ By ADAM NAGOURNEY
</P>
<P>
   Arrests in 1963 Bombing
</P>
<P>
   Justice delayed may not be justice served, but Alabama
prosecutors figure it is better than nothing. A grand jury indicted
