<P>
   DAVIDIANS-MONEY _ Who is paying the astronomical tab for the
plaintiffs' investigation and preparation leading to the civil
lawsuit? What's the cost to the taxpayers? If the government loses,
who pays what to whom? Who stands to earn the most out of a verdict
for the plaintiffs? (England, Waco Tribune-Herald). 15.
