   TV-COLUMN _ You know how I can tell when I really like a show? I
watch it when it's on. Let me explain. I tape more shows in a week
than most people probably watch in a month. Watching a series at my
convenience makes my life much easier. (Thompson, Palm Beach Post).
25.
